@startuml UC13_Sequence
title UC13: 管理课程计划 - 顺序图

actor "教务处" as AA
boundary "课程计划管理界面" as PlanForm
control "课程控制器" as CourseCtrl
entity "Course" as Course
entity "Schedule" as Schedule

AA -> PlanForm : 调整学分、教师、时间等面板
PlanForm -> CourseCtrl : updatePlan(courseId, planData)
CourseCtrl -> Schedule : checkGlobalConflict(planData)
Schedule --> CourseCtrl : noConflict

CourseCtrl -> Course : updatePlan(planData)
Course --> CourseCtrl : success
CourseCtrl --> PlanForm : 更新成功提示
PlanForm -> AA : 显示结果
@enduml
